      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Organizers</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-funded-by field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who paid for the project or initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Sopot City Council</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-funding-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Funding Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_funding_entity_kind%3A19">Local Government (e.g. Village, Town, City)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-organization field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who was primarily responsible for organizing the initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/organizations/sopot-development-initiative-sir-sopocka-inicjatywa-rozwojowa">Sopot Development Initiative (SIR- Sopocka Inicjatywa Rozwojowa)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Organizing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_implementing_entity_kind%3A20">Community Based Organization</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-initiative-support-other field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who else supported the initiative? :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Prawo ƒ∞ Sprawiedliwo≈õc (Law and Justice) and Kocham Sopot (I love Sopot) Party Councilors </div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Types of Supporting Entities:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div cla